  • Deadmau5 biography

    You probably wouldn’t recognize Joel Zimmerman in the street but there’s no doubt you would recognize the giant mouse head that’s come to represent Zimmerman’s alter ego Deadmau5.

    Anton Zaslavski was born on the 2nd of September 1989, and after taking the stage name Zedd in 2010, he has become one of the most in demand EDM producers, Dj’s and remixers in the world.

  • A$AP Ferg biography

    A$AP Ferg (born October 20 1988) is a Harlem, U.S based rapper who is most famous for being part of the A$AP Mob, a collective that features other well known rappers A$AP Rocky and A$AP Ant.

    Read more
  • Above & Beyond biography

    Above and Beyond is a British EDM group formed in London, UK in 2000. The trio consists of Jono Grant, Tony McGuiness, and Paavo Siljamäki.

    Read more
  • RL Grime biography

    RL Grime, real name Henry Steinway, is an American producer of hip hop, trap and bass music who also meddles with dubstep and electronic music. A relative newcomer, he has been working the industry since 2011.

    Read more
  • Felix Cartal biography

    Taelor Deitcher better known by his stage name Felix Cartal, is a Canadian electronic music producer and DJ originally from Vancouver.
